---

<BaseLayout
  title={seo.title}
  description={seo.description}
  ogImage={seo.ogImage}
  ogType={seo.ogType}
  keywords={seo.keywords}
  schema={schema}
>
  <!-- Add LocalBusiness schema for better local SEO -->
  <SchemaOrg
    slot="head"
    type="LocalBusiness"
    data={{
      name: 'Digital Growth Experts',
      description: 'Professional website design services in Sydney. We create custom, conversion-focused websites that help Australian businesses grow online.',
      image: `${Astro.site}images/logo.png`,
    }}
  />

  <Header />

  <main id="main-content">
    <Hero
      title={hero.title}
      subtitle={hero.subtitle}
      primaryCTA={hero.primaryCTA}
      secondaryCTA={hero.secondaryCTA}
      image={hero.image}
      imageAlt={hero.imageAlt}
    >
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Website Design That Converts Visitors Into <HighlightText color="primary" style="bold">Paying Customers</HighlightText>
      </Fragment>
    </Hero>

    <!-- Social Proof - Client Logos -->
    <ClientLogoCarousel />

    <!-- Portfolio Marquee -->
    <PortfolioMarquee
      title="Websites Built to Deliver Results"
      subtitle="Every website we create has one purpose: turning visitors into customers. Click any project to view the full case study."
      portfolioItems={portfolioItems}
      trustText="Every website is <strong>custom-designed</strong> and <strong>hand-coded</strong> for speed, <strong>SEO</strong>, and conversions. <strong>No templates</strong>. No page builders."
    >
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Websites Built to <HighlightText color="primary" style="bold">Deliver Results</HighlightText>
      </Fragment>
    </PortfolioMarquee>

    <!-- Why Website Design Matters -->
    <section class="relative py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-950 overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Decorative gradient orbs -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-6 text-white">
            Why Your Website Design Matters More Than Ever
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            94% of first impressions come down to design. With attention spans shrinking, your website has just 3 seconds to convince visitors to stay and explore.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/[0.08] rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-white/[0.15] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/10">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/10 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6 group-hover:from-blue-500/30 group-hover:to-blue-600/20 group-hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors duration-300">First Impressions Count</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Visitors form an opinion about your website in just 0.05 seconds. Professional design builds instant credibility and trust from the moment they land on your page.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/[0.08] rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-white/[0.15] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/10">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/10 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6 group-hover:from-blue-500/30 group-hover:to-blue-600/20 group-hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors duration-300">Built for Conversions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Strategic design decisions can boost conversion rates by up to 400%. Every element on your site is placed with purpose to guide visitors toward taking action.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/[0.08] rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-white/[0.15] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/10">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/10 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6 group-hover:from-blue-500/30 group-hover:to-blue-600/20 group-hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors duration-300">Mobile-First Approach</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              More than 60% of web traffic now comes from mobile devices. We design for mobile first to guarantee perfect experiences across every screen size.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 4 -->
          <div class="group relative bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/[0.08] rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-500 ease-out hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-white/[0.15] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/10">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/10 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6 group-hover:from-blue-500/30 group-hover:to-blue-600/20 group-hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors duration-300">Speed Drives Results</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              Every 1-second delay in page load time can cut conversions by 7%. Our websites load fast to keep visitors engaged and ready to convert.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Included -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display mb-6 text-gray-900">
            What You Get With Our Website Design Services
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
            Everything you need to launch a website that works as hard as you do. From initial strategy through to ongoing support, we have you covered.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900">Fully Custom Design</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              No cookie-cutter templates. Every website we build is custom-designed to reflect your brand, connect with your audience, and set you apart from competitors.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900">Mobile-First Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We build mobile-first from day one. Your website will look stunning and perform flawlessly on phones, tablets, and desktops.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900">Conversion Optimisation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Strategic CTAs, trust signals, and user flows designed to turn browsers into buyers. Every element on your site serves a clear purpose.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900"><a href="/technical-seo/" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">SEO Foundation</a></h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Technical SEO is built in from the ground up. Fast loading speeds, clean code, proper structure, and schema markup all help you rank higher in search results.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900">Lightning-Fast Loading</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Optimised images, efficient code, and modern hosting mean your website loads in under 2 seconds. This keeps visitors engaged and impresses Google.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-3 text-gray-900">Ongoing Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We stick around after launch. Ongoing maintenance, updates, and support keep your website secure and performing at its best for years to come.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Long-Form SEO Content Section -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900 mb-6">Web Design Sydney: Your Local Partner for Digital Success</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">In today's digital world, your website is often the first interaction potential customers have with your business. A beautiful website that captures attention is just the beginning. What truly matters is creating a bespoke website that drives results, builds trust, and establishes a powerful online presence for your brand. As a Sydney based agency, we understand the unique needs of Australian businesses and the local market dynamics that influence digital success.</p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Your website needs to do more than simply exist. It needs to work hard for your business every single day. That means combining stunning visual appeal with strategic functionality, ensuring your website serves as a complete digital solution that attracts, engages, and converts visitors into customers. Whether you are a startup looking to establish your first online presence or an established company ready to refresh your digital strategy, partnering with a local team offers distinct advantages.</p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">We take pride in being easy to deal with throughout every project. Our collaborative approach means you are never left wondering about progress or next steps. From initial consultation to launch day and beyond, we provide the tools you need to succeed in the competitive Sydney market and grow your business sustainably.</p>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Choose a Professional Web Design Agency</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">The difference between amateur and professional web design is immediately apparent to visitors. Professional web design agencies bring together experienced designers, developers, and strategists who understand what makes a website truly effective. While free website builders and drag and drop tools might seem appealing for their simplicity, they rarely deliver the customised, high-performing web design that competitive businesses require.</p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Working with design experts means gaining access to years of collective experience across hundreds of web design projects. This expertise translates into websites that load faster, rank higher in search engine results, and convert more visitors into paying customers. Our team follows best practices to ensure every website we create meets the highest standards for performance, accessibility, and user experience.</p>

